<PARTYBLOCK>
<LINE>BETWEEN:</LINE>
<PARTY>DAVID P. LONG</PARTY>
<PARTYROLE>RESPONDENT (PLAINTIFF)</PARTYROLE>
<CONNECTOR>AND:</CONNECTOR>
<PARTY>RED BRANCH INVESTMENTS LIMITED AND GERALD WRIGHT</PARTY>
